keys.string: Soooo, how was your first day? Exciting huh?
This isn’t my first time at college. Just my first time here.
Yeah. Machine learning sounds like it’s going to be a difficult class. I don’t know much about it, but I really like the teacher.
The other classes should be good too. I’m just hoping the work won’t overwhelm me. I don’t expect it to.
If that’s it, I’ve got some work to go back to. See you tomorrow!
I did a little bit of research on VR in my undergraduate studies, no programing though. I’m just hoping Arun doesn’t make us develop with the headset on.
I hate to admit this, but I thought the class would have more to do with weather. Don’t laugh at me, and definitely don’t tell Amini.
